{"tid":2246754,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"正呀喂！M記朱古力批同龍蝦湯19號正式回歸","createTime":"2020-10-17T10:23:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T12:02:42.000Z","uid":376170,"like":40,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e799c4d7b33f179bef92e8cccdc963ce097e3b61","tid":2246754,"uid":376170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:23:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">香港人可唔可以爭氣啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可唔可以比多啲骨氣</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YVx5Uzb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYVx5Uzb.png&h=db14d362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上年呢個時間冇武肺，正常生活，藍店真係未試過見到條龍，淨係得廢老幫襯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宜家就每晚都會見到啲藍店（e.g.元氣）排晒長龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行過M記就一定會見到有人揸住啲外賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nStarbucks 入面就永遠有班中學生係個到買杯野飲坐喺度溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲見過有中學生著住校服入紅磡冰室<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係明白大家對呢種方式開始疲勞<br />\n<br />\n但係大家可唔可以比多啲堅持，變成生活習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9bebcbf289c8f134f3b92fd505f0d4d82f1c96","tid":2246754,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:24:26.000Z","msg":"不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9595cf6d28c55f84c2506f76e4865468c8304864","tid":2246754,"uid":308615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e799c4d7b33f179bef92e8cccdc963ce097e3b61","tid